            <p>We follow your requests for your pets! (feeding times, socialization habits, comfort items at bedtime, and more)</p>
            <p>Water is accessible 24/7.</p>
            <p>Grooming and training services are available for your dog at an additional price.</p>
            <p>Pet siblings are able to stay in the same room for optimum comfort if requested. </p>
